title: Pixel 4 XL with Android 11 - My dialer will no longer search/display certain contacts.
content:
My Pixel 4 XL will no longer display certain contacts when searching from the dialer. This is the main way I search contacts to dial.

For example I should be able to type 236 and it would display BEN. It no longer does this since about 3 weeks ago. Why?
category: Contacts, Calls, Voicemail, Google Pixel 4 XL
